---
title: Chipotle Steak with Lemon and Herb Roasted New Potatoes and Broccoli
description: If we had a penny for every time we'd seen a badly cooked steak we’d probably be millionaires. Or at least rich enough to treat ourselves to dinner at a top steakhouse! Yet follow these three tips and a great result is assured at home: i) Allow the steak to come to room temperature before you cook it ii) Get your frying pan super hot iii) Rest the steak for a few minutes before you eat. Enjoy!
